 A silver Toyota Hilux LDV has been stolen from the Middelburg Mall parking area this afternoon. The registration is CYG 204 L. According to the police report, the suspects remain unidentified and it remains unknown which direction they left in. Members of the public are urged to look out  for the vehicle and if seen, to contact the 10111 call centre or alternatively, the Middelburg SAPS at 013 247 7343.     Middelburg police officer arrested during Hawks operation Botshabelo’s last song Five busted for dagga Nabbed cops granted bail  • Save our standby number (072 248 3855) and send us a WhatsApp message with the words “Add me” to be added to our broadcast list. • Like us on Facebook, follow us on Twitter and Instagram. • Subscribe to our YouTube channel. • Click on the link to subscribe to our bi-weekly newsletter via email. Contact our news room on our 24 hr standby number 072 248 3855, or send a mail to our editor tobie@mobserver.co.za